# =========================
# Mined corpus priors — regenerated locally from datasets you obtain.
# NOT committed: keeps the repo free of anything derived from third-party
# datasets (see DATA_LICENSES.md). The dir READMEs are kept.
# =========================
backend/app/priors/*.json
backend/app/priors/grooves/*.json

# Raw MIDI datasets must never be committed (song-transcription corpora are
# copyrighted; keep the repo data-free).
*.mid
*.midi